# Proof Engine Skill
#
# When the user asks to prove, verify, fact-check, or rigorously establish
# whether a claim is true or false, follow the Proof Engine skill.
#
# Setup: Set PROOF_ENGINE_ROOT to the absolute path of the skill/ directory
# in this repository.
#
# Instructions: Read and follow skill/SKILL.md
#
# Trigger phrases: "is it really true", "can you prove", "verify this",
# "fact-check this", "prove it", "show me the logic"
#
# Do NOT use for opinions, essays, or questions with no verifiable answer.
#
# Key scripts are in skill/scripts/:
#   computations.py, extract_values.py, smart_extract.py,
#   verify_citations.py, validate_proof.py, source_credibility.py
